    dcterms:description "NanoCover Bath + Tiles provide an invisible layer so dirt and lime residue cannot get stuck. It is typically used on sanitary porcelain, glazed tiles, polished granite, interior windows and glass in the home. dirt and lime can be removed with a wet cloth afterwards!" ;
    ochv:C0034030 [ dcterms:description "perception metrics data for PROD_2250" ] .

