    obo:MESH_D012306 [ dcterms:description "risk assessment data for PROD_2251" ] ;
    dcterms:description " NanoCover Car Glass is a product with many advantages. On the one hand, it makes rain very light beads and makes the removal of dirt and insect residues from the windshield easier. Firstly, in the rain you get a considerably better view. The use of wipers becomes almost superfluous when driving over 70 km / h, as the rain, which drops as drops on the seal, flies off due to wind resistance." ;
    ochv:C0034030 [ dcterms:description "perception metrics data for PROD_2251" ] .

