    dcterms:description "Glass Sealing SR / Universal is a chemical nano-seal for the treatment of windows, shop windows, glass panels, etc. The seal has \"slip-light\" properties which make dirt more difficult to bind on the sealed surfaces. Cleaning nano-sealed glass panels requires less time and less use of chemical cleaners." ;
