    dcterms:description "“Nano Bath - Glass and Tile Seal” is intended for non-absorbent surfaces in the bathroom. The sealant protects against lime, bacteria and liquids. The product is a nanobased surface sealing product specially designed for bathrooms, the surface will, after treatment, reject water and oily liquids." ;
