    dcterms:description "Nano-technology based long-lasting sealant for paintwork or painted plastic components. The paintwork is protected by a coating of modified fluorocarbon nano-particles, which are as hard as glass. It freshens up the colours intensively, has a dirt repellent effect, and has an outstanding droplet run off effect. Depending on conditions, provides protection for up to 9 months." ;
    ochv:C0034030 [ dcterms:description "perception metrics data for PROD_2314" ] .

