    obo:CHMO_0000101 "\"All our products have undergone extensive laboratory tests to international standards, confirming their effectiveness against bacteria such as Staphylococcus aureus, Bacillus megaterium, Bacillus subtilis, Escherichia coli, Pseudomonas fluorescens and Methicillin-resistant Staphylococcus Aureus (MRSA). In all cases the results show that greater than 99.9% of all bacteria are destroyed within 24 hours.\" (See: http://agactive.com/faq.html) \"100% guaranteed to kill bacteria and control odor\"" ;
    obo:MESH_D012306 [ dcterms:description "risk assessment data for PROD_2543" ] ;
    dcterms:description "Currently six styles of socks are being sold: business, anklet-b, anklet-c, anklet-w, crew and quarter.  This company also sellshand and bath towels, sheet and pillow case sets, pet blankets, and antibacterial spray (See: http://agactive.com/products.html). The website cites Silversure technology as the specific type of nanosilver technology they use, but no outside sources can be found." ;
    ochv:C0034030 [ dcterms:description "perception metrics data for PROD_2543" ] .

